data.description: This well maintained and exquisite home is the perfect 3 bedroom 2.5 bath that you have been looking for. Located with easy access to HWY 121, I-35, the Dallas North Tollway, and the President Bush Expressway, you will have ease of access to anywhere you need to go. So much shopping and dining available nearby for you to enjoy. No carpet!!! This home comes with many updates and features to include Windows replaced in 2023, HVAC unit in 2023, and the owners suite bathroom was just recently remodeled. No pesky HOA to deal with and the greenbelt behind the home means less neighbors as well. The soaring ceilings provide that large home feeling. Relax in the living room and enjoy the fireplace anytime you want to! The utility room boasts a second pantry which is great for extra storage. Enjoy the rear covered patio when you feel like grilling or just spending some time in the oversized back yard. This home has so much to offer. Schedule you private tour today!
